Seeing as bobcat has ended support for his old soyuz, i have taken the liberty of re-relasing it so that you have a craft to resupply salyut station.

EDIT: DOWNLOADS ARE UP. Also, i added a stock tiangong

Shenzhou has placeholder OM.

Download: https://onedrive.live.com/redir?resid=B6FE8325EF32F465!1166&authkey=!AKCusY0auickCHI&ithint=file%2c.zip

Edited July 1, 2014 by TheBigCon4800

This subforum is for releases only. You should only start a thread here when you have something for us to download. Anyway, how will you get a Shenzhou and a Zond? AFAIK none of those were in Bobcat's mods.
